'''Ameccaq''' neɣ '''Astum''' gar n sin n [[agaz (tanzeggit)|wagazen]] d [[teɣzi (tusnakt)|teɣzi]] n [[amaɣad (tusnakt)|uzerrig amaɣad]] gar n sin n wagazen-a. Tikwal tettili-d tenfalit ɣef umeccaq s yirem n [[akud|wakud]] issefken i wakken ad tiddel s tikli neɣ s temseddut (aɣanib-a yeṭṭafar isemrasen iyalassen. maca mači ussniwen, acku ur yelli ara d ufrin). Dɣa [[tafat]] tettwasled deg wanecta acku tazzla-ines d timbeddit (s unect n [[tiẓri tamassaɣt]]) ɣef wanecta i ttwasidnen imeccaqen isnallunen s [[afawatay|ifawatayen]] (ameccaq i tetteddu tafat deg useggas) s talɣa tussnant. 

Ameccaq yettwasnes deg [[afaris (tusnakt)|ufaris]] (Tallunt × Tallunt) ar wuṭṭunen imdettiyen ilawen, ayen yennumken asnas yeqqnen yal sin n wagazen deg tallunt s wuṭṭun imdetti ilaw. Asnas-a ittfaras-d timentilin-a: 

* <math>\forall (x,y)\in E^2 : d(x,y)=d(y,x)</math> (arawas)
* <math>\forall (x,y)\in E^2 : d(x,y)=0\Leftrightarrow x=y</math> (abeṭṭay)
* <math>\forall (x,y,z)\in E^3 : d(x,z)\leq d(x,y)+d(y,z)</math> ([[Tanmeglit takeṛdisant]])

